hopobject.body: Will I have to work shifts? lumabelle skin cream Wardak is a restive province in eastern Afghanistan.  Earlier this year, Afghan President Hamid Karzai ordered all U.S. Special Forces out of the region, after accusations of improper conduct.  Afghan forces are now responsible for all security in the province, but are often accompanied on missions by American troops, whose mandate is to advise and assist when requested.
